These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-1::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, dressmaker
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: surfing, soccer
1. the dressmaker is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is surfing##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Job           | dressmaker | designer |
| Sport   | soccer     | surfing  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-2::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: collecting, writing
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, motorbike
1. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |
| Hobby         | writing   | collecting      |
| Transport   | airplane | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-3::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  police-officer, musician
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, subway
1. the police-officer is somewhere to the right of the person driving the boat##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2    |
| Job   | musician | police-officer    |
| Transport     | boat | subway |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-4::.
