.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-9::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: september, november
2 different pets are kept: fish, hedgehog
1. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the right of the owner of the fish##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2     |
| Birthday   | november | september |
| Pet        | fish  | hedgehog |

